Invocation Name: lunch lady
des:
Have the kids ask the Alexa lunch lady what's for lunch! 

Lunch Lady will provide a readout of the Ascension Parish School Board lunch menu for any given day. Just ask "lunch lady what's for lunch?" Want to know about tomorrow or next Friday, just ask? 

"Alexa ask lunch lady what's for lunch tomorrow?"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
